Recently sold: $350,000. Lovely end-unit townhome in Eagan. description: Recently sold: $316,000.

Recently sold: $399,900. Impeccably maintained 2 Story in the perfect location on manicured treed lot.  Immediately you can feel the care taken by this one owner home.  Concrete drive, hard edged landscape, and perfectly maintained.  Additional side parking for overflow vehicles.  Over 3100 SF of thoughtful spaces and warmth flow through this home.  Three large upper level bedrooms feature large master with balcony office access.  The baths were maximized to use as one or separate for multiple users.  Plenty of storage and closet space throughout.  The main floor has multiple sitting areas depending on your desires.  Main Floor family room, living/dining combination, and the tree side porch.  gas fireplace w/ rustic brick surround, open kitchen with quartz tops and newer stainless appliances.  Nice mud room off spacious double stall garage.  Lower level office, entertainment area, large 3/4 bath, and plenty of storage.  Note condition of mechanicals and storage details.  The yard is something to behold!

Recently sold: $250,000. Premium townhome in a quiet central location in Eagan. South facing for lots of natural light and a natural heated driveway effect for melting snow in the winter. The kitchen has been remodeled with granite countertops including new sink and faucet, and brand new stainless appliances, a new laminate kitchen floor was also installed this year. The upstairs bathroom has  been updated with new fixtures and shower enclosure, plus new vanity and natural travertine flooring. New laminate floors were installed on the upper level and new tile and laminate on the lower level. Beautiful  new oak stairs leading to the newly finished lower level are sure to please. There is a new 50 gallon water heater and new water softener new garage door and opener. All the windows have been replaced with high quality wood windows, the sliding patio door was replaced at the same time as the windows. The front door was replaced this year and so was the washer and dryer. The roof has been replaced in the last five years. There will be many years of trouble free living in your new townhome!

Two car attached garage. School District #196 Rosemount-Apple Valley-Eagan. Rental Screening Guidelines:
Background and Credit Checks are conducted on all adults
